CustomField.description: Defines if the ability to add multiple Mark Up / Margin Rates to a Rate Calculator is enabled. If False, there will only be 1 set of Mark Up / Margin Rates applied to the Rate Calculator.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: Defines if the ability to add multiple Mark Up / Margin Rates to a Rate Calculator is enabled. If False, there will only be 1 set of Mark Up / Margin Rates applied to the Rate Calculator.
CustomField.label: Enable add Mark Up / Margin function
